data.description: Enjoy Florida living at its finest in The Cove at Falcon Trace, a gated community with resort style pool! This 2020 CBS construction home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms & a split floor plan for ultimate privacy. Entertain in style w/ modern touches like tile flooring, high ceilings, upgraded kitchen w/ island, granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. Find sanctuary in the expansive primary suite with dual sinks, 2 walk-in closets & a luxurious full tile shower. Outside, relax on the covered patio in your spacious fully fenced yard. Complete with a paver driveway & hurricane shutters
